        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "Labor Department of Chhattisgarh State started this scheme &amp;quot;Safai Karmakar Prasuti Sahayata Yojana&amp;quot; for unorganized worker on  11 March 2015. The main objective of the scheme to empower unorganized worker by providing financial assistance for Maternity Assistance. \n",
        "benefits_md": "\n- Female employees will receive a financial assistance of ₹4,200 in the third month of pregnancy and ₹2,800 in the eighth month of pregnancy as maternity benefit.\n- Male employees will receive a financial assistance of ₹3,000 as paternity leave after the birth of the child.\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "Chhattisgarh State Government started a scheme \"Safai Karmakar Prasuti Sahayata Yojana\" for unorganized worker on 11 March 2015.",
